summary: For long time i all ways loved bricks , brick walls , brick roads , brick bridge's , so this is kind of a test to see how people like roads made out of bricks , i may do a update and add more roads and bridge's if people like my work  .
descriptionHtml:
New 1.3 is out , just a new brick texture i been working on , now the texture's  have the _n and _h file with it , which helps a little , you can see from new screen shots that the sun , shines off the bricks now which give it a slight 3d look . I still have a lot work to do to make the perfect brick roads and bridges i want , i am learning from a few people for tip's , but may take more time to make better brick stuff ! All Textures are in 1k size for now !

New version of Brick roads and bridge's 1.2 is out , i feel 1.1 was to cartoonish , i'm sure other agree , i hope every one likes this version a little bit better ! Lit me no if you like it !

Brick roads and bridge's now in skyrim ! I love brick roads and thought i try to make a mod , that will add more modern life in to skyrim !  . I might update to make the roads more life like , but for now i hope this will due , please lit me no if there is any issues i need to fix , and what i can do to make the mod better . I spent some time looking for the right textures , all textures are in 1k format for now , so it should be ok on a low end computer !
